Multi-Arch: foreign
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         ${shlibs:Depends},
         libdbus-cpp4 (= ${binary:Version})
Description: header-only dbus-binding leveraging C++-11
 Protocol compiler and generator to automatically generate protocol headers from
 introspection XML.

